snippet.title: GANBARIDE! Retro Trading Card Arcade Game! Kamen Rider Battle: Ganbaride!
snippet.description:
Here is more Kamen Rider Battle: Ganbaride the arcade game with trading cards! If you have seen Animal Kaiser or Hero of Robots you'll know what to expect! This game spits out trading cards that you can use to select your heroes to play with. It also seems to take special coins that strengthen your abilitys, but I was not given any coins! If anyone has played this game and knows more about the coins, please let me know in the comments!

If you like this video please Like/Share/Subscribe, it will help us become king of the Power Rangers!:)
